fields.headline: Genius crossword No 142
fields.bodyText: Seventeen solutions, not further defined in their clues, are partners in well-known pairings. The grid entry for these clues needs to be the other partner in the pair. Letter counts are for the word to be entered. (5) 19 Serious change in speed, then another (9) 23 Daisy’s partner steals one pound (8) 24 Expert bricklayer?
